      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How do I convert Ah to Wh?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "To convert Ah to Wh, multiply amp hours by the battery voltage. Formula: Ah x V = Wh. For kWh, divide the result by 1,000. Example: a 125Ah battery at 12.5V gives 125 x 12.5 = 1562.5Wh, or roughly 1.5kWh."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
